    "en": {
      "title": "An invalid ballot was caught",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Voting for the presidential election is over. Currently counting of valid votes is underway.",
        "Out of which, even till 12 noon, one ballot was allotted in the invalid ballot box.",
        "Harin Fernando on behalf of the presidential candidate Ranil Wickremesinghe and Dylan Fernando on behalf of Dallas Beauty will count the votes. On behalf of Anurakumara Dissanayake, Vijitha Herath is also monitoring."
      ],
